STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jerrel E. WILLIAMS, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0244 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Jerrel Williams appeals his conviction for possession with intent to deliver crack cocaine. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
